<body>
<div><head>和苞漢趙記</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-1a.2">劉聰嘉平三年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-1a.3">廷尉陳元達極諫。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-1a.4">聰怒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-1a.5">將斬之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-1a.6">聰時幸逍遙園李中堂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-1a.7">元達抱堂下樹叫曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-1a.8">「臣所言者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-1a.9">社稷之計，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-1a.10">聰勉聽之。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-1a.11">於是易李堂為愧賢堂。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-1a.12">《初學記》二十四、《御覽》百七十六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.2">魯陽侯王廣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.3">字廣之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.4">為西揚州刺史。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.5">晉末，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.6">聚眾避也為蠻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.7">梅芳扇動山夷圍廣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.8">城陷，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.9">蠻囚廣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.10">將詣芳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.11">廣女有美色，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.12">芳引入，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.13">甚有寵。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.14">入經一旬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.15">王伺芳睡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.16">引刀斬芳。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.17">芳驚起曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.18">「何故反耶！」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.19">王罵曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.20">「蠻畜！<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.21">我欲誅反賊等，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.22">何謂我反乎？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.23">吾聞父仇不同天，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.24">母仇不同地。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.25">汝反逆無狀，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.26">害人父母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.27">而復無禮淩人。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.28">吾所以不死者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.29">欲誅汝耳。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.30">今死自吾分，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.31">不待汝殺我。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.32">但恨不得梟汝首於通逵，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.33">以塞大恥！」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.34">辭氣猛厲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.35">色無變容，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.36">乃自殺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.37">時年十五。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-2a.38">《御覽》四十。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.2">今上殺晉散騎常侍梁緯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.3">召妻辛氏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.4">伏地大哭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.5">仰白今上曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.6">「妾聞女不再醮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.7">男以義烈。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.8">聞妾夫已死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.9">理無獨生。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.10">就辟有司，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.11">地下以事舅姑，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.12">且婦人再娉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.13">明公亦安用哉！」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.14">遂號哭不止。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.15">止曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.16">「貞婦也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.17">其任之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.18">亦自殺。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-3a.19">《御覽》四百四十。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.2">劉聰麟嘉三年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.3">太子粲討趙同、郭默於洛陽。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.4">默使耿稚等夜北渡河，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.5">襲太子營，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.6">飛梯騰柵而入。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.7">太子勒兵於東北，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.8">穿柵而去。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.9">《御覽》三百三十六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.10">今止光初二年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.11">石勒召幽冀之眾十餘萬人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.12">造攻車飛梯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.13">攻平陽小城。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.14">今上遣騎萬五千，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.15">曳迆揚塵，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.16">曀於山谷，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.17">尋汾州向平陽內外擊之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.18">勒師潰。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-4a.19">《御覽》三百三十六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-5a.2">光初六年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-5a.3">今上討陳安陽隴城，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-5a.4">城內得安死。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-5a.5">陳安奮刀，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-5a.6">左右俱發。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-5a.7">隴上語曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-5a.8">「隴上壯士有陳安，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-5a.9">丈八蛇矛左右槃。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-5a.10">《御覽》四百九十六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.2">劉淵徙治平陽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.3">於汾水中得白玉璽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.4">廣四寸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.5">高二分，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.6">龍紐，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.7">文曰「有新保之」。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.8">《事類賦注》九。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.9">《御覽》八百四。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.10">按：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.11">以下皆引作《趙書》，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.12">疑亦和苞之書。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.13">蓋《田融趙書》怕記石事，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.14">所以一曰《二石集記》，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.15">不言及漢趙。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.16">故附於漢趙記之後，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-6a.17">以俟攷。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-7a" ed="CHANT" n="001-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-7a.2">趙染龍長安。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-7a.3">秦王業奔射鴈樓，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-7a.4">格戢至天明，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-7a.5">不拔。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-7a.6">《御覽》百七十六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-7a.7">劉曜於龍門河水中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-7a.8">得一玉璽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-7a.9">文云「剋壽永昌」。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-7a.10">以為天錫神璽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-7a.11">齋九日而受之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-7a.12">《書鈔》百三十一、《御覽》六百八十二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a" ed="CHANT" n="001-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.2">劉曜討陳安於隴城下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.3">小將劉牙、趙牢、路松、多堅戍。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.4">不下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.5">城內得安死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.6">乃亮曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.7">「隴上健兒曰陳安，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.8">軀幹雖小腹中寬。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.9">愛養將士同心肝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.10">騄驄駿馬鐵鏤鞍。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.11">七尺大刀配齊鐶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.12">丈八蛇矛左右盤。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.13">十盪十決無當前。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.14">百騎俱出如雲浮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.15">追者千萬騎悠悠。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.16">戰始三交八蛇矛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.17">十騎俱蕩九騎留。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.18">棄我騄驄攀巖悲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.19">天大降雨追者休。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.20">阿呵呼嗚呼柰子乎！<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.21">嗚呼阿呵柰子何！」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1302_CHANT_001-8a.22">《御覽》三百五十三、又四百六十五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
